/* дәӨжҚўиҜҰжғ…йЎөйқў - зҙ«иүІйң“иҷ№зҒҜйЈҺж јз»ҹдёҖ */

.container {
  padding: 24rpx;
  padding-bottom: 160rpx;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  min-height: 100vh;
  background: #020208;
  position: relative;
}

.container::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.12) 0%, transparent 50%),
              radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(123, 104, 238, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

/* дәӨжҚўеӨҙйғЁеҚЎзүҮ */
.exchange-header {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12, 12, 28, 0.95) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 15, 0.98) 100%);
  border-radius: 24rpx;
  padding: 32rpx;
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.25);
  box-shadow: 0 0 25rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15),
              0 8rpx 32rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20rpx);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.exchange-header::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 2rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
    transparent 0%, 
    rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.6) 20%,
    rgba(186, 85, 211, 0.6) 50%,
    rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.6) 80%,
    transparent 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 0 15rpx rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.4);
}

.exchange-visual {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.exchange-item {
  flex: 1;
  text-align: center;
}

.item-label {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 56rpx;
  height: 56rpx;
  line-height: 56rpx;
  text-align: center;
  border-radius: 12rpx;
  font-size: 28rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 16rpx;
  box-shadow: 0 4rpx 12rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

.exchange-item.want .item-label {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3) 0%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2) 100%);
  color: #60a5fa;
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
}

.exchange-item.have .item-label {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3) 0%, rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.2) 100%);
  color: #4ade80;
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
}

.item-text {
  display: block;
  font-size: 30rpx;
  color: #f8fafc;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.4;
  text-shadow: 0 0 10rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.2);
}

.exchange-arrow {
  width: 80rpx;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 40rpx;
  color: #c8a2ff;
  text-shadow: 0 0 15rpx rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.5);
  animation: arrowPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes arrowPulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.7; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}

.status-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.status-tag {
  padding: 10rpx 20rpx;
  border-radius: 12rpx;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  border: 1rpx solid;
}

.status-tag.pending {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2) 0%, rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.1) 100%);
  color: #4ade80;
  border-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
  box-shadow: 0 0 15rpx rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
}

.status-tag.matched {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2) 0%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1) 100%);
  color: #60a5fa;
  border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
  box-shadow: 0 0 15rpx rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
}

.status-tag.completed {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.2) 0%, rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.1) 100%);
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  border-color: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
}

.create-time {
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}

/* з”ЁжҲ·еҚЎзүҮ */
.user-card {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 24rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12, 12, 28, 0.95) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 15, 0.98) 100%);
  border-radius: 24rpx;
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.25);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15),
              0 8rpx 32rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.user-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 2rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
    transparent 0%, 
    rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.5) 20%,
    rgba(186, 85, 211, 0.5) 50%,
    rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.5) 80%,
    transparent 100%);
}

.user-avatar {
  width: 80rpx;
  height: 80rpx;
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin-right: 20rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.4);
  box-shadow: 0 4rpx 16rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.2);
}

.user-info {
  flex: 1;
}

.user-name {
  display: block;
  font-size: 30rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #f8fafc;
  margin-bottom: 4rpx;
}

.user-school {
  display: block;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}

.follow-btn {
  padding: 16rpx 24rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.2) 0%, rgba(186, 85, 211, 0.15) 100%);
  color: #c8a2ff;
  border-radius: 30rpx;
  font-size: 28rpx;
  font-weight: 500;
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.4);
  box-shadow: 0 4rpx 16rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.2);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.follow-btn:active {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.3) 0%, rgba(186, 85, 211, 0.25) 100%);
  transform: scale(0.98);
}

/* еӣҫзүҮеҢәеҹҹ */
.image-section {
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.section-title {
  display: block;
  font-size: 30rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #f8fafc;
  margin-bottom: 16rpx;
  text-shadow: 0 0 10rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.2);
}

.image-grid {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 16rpx;
}

.item-image {
  width: 200rpx;
  height: 200rpx;
  border-radius: 20rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.3);
  box-shadow: 0 4rpx 16rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.2);
}

/* жҸҸиҝ°еҢәеҹҹ */
.desc-section {
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  padding: 24rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12, 12, 28, 0.95) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 15, 0.98) 100%);
  border-radius: 24rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.25);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15),
              0 8rpx 32rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.desc-section::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 2rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
    transparent 0%, 
    rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.5) 20%,
    rgba(186, 85, 211, 0.5) 50%,
    rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.5) 80%,
    transparent 100%);
}

.desc-text {
  font-size: 28rpx;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* дҝЎжҒҜеҚЎзүҮ */
.info-card {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12, 12, 28, 0.95) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 15, 0.98) 100%);
  border-radius: 24rpx;
  padding: 24rpx;
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.25);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15),
              0 8rpx 32rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.info-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 2rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, 
    transparent 0%, 
    rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.5) 20%,
    rgba(186, 85, 211, 0.5) 50%,
    rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.5) 80%,
    transparent 100%);
}

.info-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 16rpx 0;
  border-bottom: 1rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15);
}

.info-row:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.info-label {
  font-size: 28rpx;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}

.info-value {
  font-size: 28rpx;
  color: #f8fafc;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.info-value.fee {
  color: #fbbf24;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-shadow: 0 0 10rpx rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
}

/* ж ҮзӯҫеҢәеҹҹ */
.tags-section {
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.tag-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 16rpx;
}

.tag {
  padding: 12rpx 24rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15) 0%, rgba(186, 85, 211, 0.1) 100%);
  color: #c8a2ff;
  border-radius: 30rpx;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.3);
  box-shadow: 0 2rpx 8rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.1);
}

/* еҢ№й…ҚеҢәеҹҹ */
.match-section {
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.match-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16rpx;
}

.match-card {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12, 12, 28, 0.95) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 15, 0.98) 100%);
  border-radius: 20rpx;
  padding: 20rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.25);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15),
              0 8rpx 32rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.match-card:active {
  transform: scale(0.98);
  border-color: rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.4);
}

.match-content {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

.match-label {
  width: 40rpx;
  height: 40rpx;
  line-height: 40rpx;
  text-align: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3) 0%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2) 100%);
  color: #60a5fa;
  border-radius: 8rpx;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  margin-right: 12rpx;
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
}

.match-label.have {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3) 0%, rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.2) 100%);
  color: #4ade80;
  border-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
}

.match-text {
  font-size: 28rpx;
  color: #f8fafc;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.match-arrow {
  width: 40rpx;
  text-align: center;
  color: #c8a2ff;
  font-size: 28rpx;
}

.match-rate {
  padding: 8rpx 16rpx;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.2) 0%, rgba(186, 85, 211, 0.15) 100%);
  color: #c8a2ff;
  border-radius: 12rpx;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.3);
}

/* дәӨжҚўи®°еҪ• */
.exchange-records {
  margin-bottom: 24rpx;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.record-list {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(12, 12, 28, 0.95) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 15, 0.98) 100%);
  border-radius: 24rpx;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.25);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15),
              0 8rpx 32rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
}

.record-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 20rpx 24rpx;
  border-bottom: 1rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.15);
}

.record-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.record-avatar {
  width: 56rpx;
  height: 56rpx;
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin-right: 16rpx;
  border: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.3);
}

.record-info {
  flex: 1;
}

.record-name {
  display: block;
  font-size: 28rpx;
  color: #f8fafc;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.record-time {
  display: block;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}

.record-status {
  padding: 8rpx 16rpx;
  border-radius: 12rpx;
  font-size: 24rpx;
  font-weight: 500;
  border: 1rpx solid;
}

.record-status.pending {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2) 0%, rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1) 100%);
  color: #fbbf24;
  border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
}

.record-status.accepted {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2) 0%, rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.1) 100%);
  color: #4ade80;
  border-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
}

.record-status.rejected {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2) 0%, rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.1) 100%);
  color: #f87171;
  border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
}

/* еә•йғЁж“ҚдҪңж ?*/
.action-bar {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 24rpx 24rpx calc(24rpx + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(2, 2, 8, 0) 0%, rgba(5, 5, 15, 0.98) 20%, rgba(5, 5, 15, 1) 100%);
  border-top: 2rpx solid rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.2);
  box-sizing: border-box;
  z-index: 999;
  backdrop-filter: blur(20rpx);
}

.action-left {
  display: flex;
  gap: 48rpx;
}

.action-item {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.action-item:active {
  transform: scale(0.95);
}

.action-icon {
  font-size: 44rpx;
  color: #c8a2ff;
  text-shadow: 0 0 15rpx rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.4);
}

.action-text {
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  margin-top: 8rpx;
}

.action-right {
  flex: 1;
  margin-left: 48rpx;
}

.apply-btn {
  width: 100%;
  height: 88rpx;
  line-height: 88rpx;
  text-align: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #9370db 30%, #ba55d3 70%, #c8a2ff 100%);
  color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 44rpx;
  font-size: 30rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  border: 1rpx solid rgba(200, 162, 255, 0.5);
  box-shadow: 0 0 25rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.5),
              0 8rpx 24rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  text-shadow: 0 0 10rpx rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.apply-btn::after {
  border: none;
}

.apply-btn:active {
  transform: scale(0.98);
  box-shadow: 0 0 35rpx rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.6),
              0 8rpx 24rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
}

.apply-btn.disabled {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3) 0%, rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.2) 100%);
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  border-color: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
  box-shadow: none;
  text-shadow: none;
}





